joelib2.smarts.bondexpr.QueryBond

Packages that use QueryBond
joelib2.smarts Provides classes for searching substructures in chemical structures based on the Smiles ARbitrary Target Specification (SMARTS) standard []. 
joelib2.smarts.bondexpr Provides classes for SMARTS bond types.
